  "texts": [
    "For tasks that involve intricate logic, a single code snippet may prove inadequate, necessitating the collaboration of multiple code snippets.",
    "Unfortunately, LLM's performance in automatically generating such code collections is suboptimal, and the existing limitations on LLM's input-output length make it challenging to handle large-scale and complex logic code [50].",
    "To mitigate these challenges, one possible approach is to modularize complex algorithmic logic by designing a universal modular design and generation method that can decompose complex tasks.",
    "Alternatively, a more user-friendly and straightforward approach could involve developing an interactive interface that allows users to determine how tasks should be decomposed.",
    "Subsequently, LLM and EA can generate code for each subtask accordingly."
  ],
